        "message": "Patch Set 9: Code-Review-1\n\nOk rancher is missing, but that will be separate commit?\n\nAnd now naming of containers changed. That affects to Molecule tests. In rancher I have been changing the container naming to the format\nrancher-server rancher-agent \nI.e. if name contains 2 or more words was using minus \"-\" separator.\nIt can be whatever but let's align is everywhere.\nI prefer - over underscore _.",
